snippet.title: Up Hike - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist "Up Hike" on Steam to get notified when the game releases! 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2767280/Up_Hike/?curator_clanid=4777282 

Up Hike is a precision platform where your goal is to climb to the top of a mountain. Jump between platforms and bounce to the walls to gain height while avoiding falling.
Every jump matters, but remember... The higher you go the harder you fall.
